                        <h3>How do I make a payment using Mobile Money payment option?</h3>
                        <p>In order to make a payment using your Mobile money transfer service, please go through the following steps depending on your service provider: </p>
                        <h2><strong>SAFARICOM</strong></h2>
                        <ol>
                            <li>Go to the M-PESA menu on your phone</li>
                            <li>Select Pay Bill option</li>
                            <li>Enter <strong>750878</strong> as the TILL Number</li>
                            <li>Enter the total amount (e.g KSh 104999)</li>
                            <li>Enter your PIN and then send the money</li>
                            <li>You will receive a transaction confirmation SMS from M-PESA</li>
                            <li>Enter the returned M-PESA Transaction ID in the provided box</li>
                        </ol>
                        <p>Once payment is received, you will receive a confirmation of your order by email. </p>

